== Births == * [[:en:Kaei|Kaei]] 5th year（[[Gregorian calendar]] [[1852]] [[November 26]]） – Yamamoto Gonnohyōe, the 16th and 22nd Prime Minister of Japan and an Admiral (d. [[1933]]). * [[:en:Keiō|Keiō]] 2nd year ([[Gregorian calendar]] [[1866]] [[November 21]]） – The first Konishiki Hachijukichi, the 17th Yokozuna (d. [[1914]]). * [[Meiji era|Meiji]] 5th year ([[Gregorian calendar]] [[1872]] [[November 15]]） – Okamoto Kido, a novelist (d. [[1939]]).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Tenshō (Momoyama period)|Tenshō Era]] 1st year ([[Julian calendar]] [[1573]] [[November 9]]） – Shimazu Katsuhisa, the 14th head of the Shimazu Clan (born [[1503]]).
